WEBVTT

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:02.950
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:05.829
joining me today. Praise the Lord. Well,

00:00:05.839 --> 00:00:07.829
I've seen a lot today.

00:00:07.839 --> 00:00:09.750
Just like I always do, I take communion

00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:11.790
and I drive around and pray in the

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:13.789
spirit.

00:00:13.799 --> 00:00:17.950
I passed the fire station on my

00:00:17.960 --> 00:00:22.230
right, and as I passed

00:00:22.230 --> 00:00:22.240
it,

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:24.590
I heard

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:27.349
'911,

00:00:27.349 --> 00:00:27.359
911.'I

00:00:27.359 --> 00:00:30.990
saw the emergency responders

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.990
responding to an emergency: major

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.630
turbulence ahead. I looked at the

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:40.790
fire station and I thought, 'Lord,

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:43.350
what's going on?'All of a sudden,

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:46.389
I went into deep groaning and travail in

00:00:46.389 --> 00:00:46.399
the spirit,

00:00:46.399 --> 00:00:49.389
praying in the spirit.

00:00:49.399 --> 00:00:52.389
The Lord started to speak to

00:00:52.399 --> 00:00:55.830
me very strongly.

00:00:55.830 --> 00:00:55.840
He

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:59.830
started showing me a

00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:01.950
Pearl Harbor

00:01:01.960 --> 00:01:05.710
event as we see in the days

00:01:05.720 --> 00:01:08.830
ahead. China is

00:01:08.830 --> 00:01:08.840
becoming

00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:11.510
desperate, and North

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:15.109
Korea is becoming desperate, wanting

00:01:15.119 --> 00:01:18.230
out from underneath the Western boot.

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:22.590
I saw North

00:01:22.590 --> 00:01:22.600
Korea—because

00:01:22.600 --> 00:01:26.030
they are the social

00:01:26.040 --> 00:01:31.270
pariah—becoming

00:01:31.280 --> 00:01:34.469
the person rising up to

00:01:34.479 --> 00:01:37.710
become the bully. Does that make sense?

00:01:37.710 --> 00:01:37.720
It's

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:41.510
like

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:44.230
the head mafia guy who has

00:01:44.240 --> 00:01:46.469
his little thugs underneath him that do

00:01:46.479 --> 00:01:48.789
the bidding for the head

00:01:48.799 --> 00:01:50.830
mafia leader. Like the

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:53.590
Godfather, and then the Godfather has

00:01:53.590 --> 00:01:53.600
henchmen.

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:55.670
He has the guys underneath him

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:58.310
that carry out the bad things.

00:01:58.320 --> 00:02:01.830
China was the Godfather, and North

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:05.270
Korea was the

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:07.590
hitman. That's what I was

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:08.869
seeing; it's the only way I can

00:02:08.879 --> 00:02:10.309
describe

00:02:10.319 --> 00:02:14.470
what I saw. I saw North Korea

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:18.229
being the pawn because of

00:02:18.239 --> 00:02:21.350
the political side of China

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:24.390
having its fingers in all the

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:27.030
different countries. They didn't want to

00:02:27.040 --> 00:02:29.750
be looked at as the bad guy for what's

00:02:29.760 --> 00:02:32.390
about to take place. But I kept hearing

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:36.110
when I was praying, 'Remember Pearl

00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:38.790
Harbor. Remember Pearl

00:02:38.790 --> 00:02:38.800
Harbor.'I

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:41.110
said, 'Lord, I

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:43.509
know that Japan was with Pearl Harbor

00:02:43.519 --> 00:02:45.190
and all that.'And He said, 'This will

00:02:45.200 --> 00:02:47.270
be a type and shadow in the days ahead.

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:50.630
Remember

00:02:50.630 --> 00:02:50.640
this.'As

00:02:50.640 --> 00:02:53.270
I was interceding, the Lord was

00:02:53.280 --> 00:02:56.509
showing me even deeper

00:02:56.519 --> 00:03:02.670
into the Asian culture as a

00:03:02.680 --> 00:03:05.430
whole. They think differently than the

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:07.070
Western

00:03:07.080 --> 00:03:09.670
culture. Do you know what I'm saying?

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:11.270
That's the only way I can

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:13.350
describe this to you. It's

00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:15.830
kind of like how the African American culture

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:17.750
thinks differently than the white

00:03:17.760 --> 00:03:19.990
American culture. Does that make sense?

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:21.910
Everybody thinks it's

00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:26.790
just culture, but I saw in this the

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:29.589
Asians sticking with their culture,

00:03:29.599 --> 00:03:32.789
trying to preserve what they believe and

00:03:32.789 --> 00:03:32.799
their

00:03:32.799 --> 00:03:35.589
family ties.

00:03:35.599 --> 00:03:37.750
It's a very Asian thing.

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:40.949
I saw China being backed

00:03:40.949 --> 00:03:40.959
into

00:03:40.959 --> 00:03:44.190
a hole, and I saw a great

00:03:44.200 --> 00:03:46.869
depression, a financial infrastructure

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:50.229
crumbling. As this happened, they

00:03:50.239 --> 00:03:54.110
didn't want to lose their

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:56.789
'Asianness,'their

00:03:56.799 --> 00:03:58.789
culture,

00:03:58.789 --> 00:03:58.799
or

00:03:58.799 --> 00:04:00.990
what they believed

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:05.110
in. So they were in a place like a

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:07.910
samurai warrior ready to

00:04:07.920 --> 00:04:09.990
turn its sword on itself. You

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:12.630
want to die with honor;

00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:14.789
you don't want to die

00:04:14.799 --> 00:04:18.390
looking disgraceful.

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:19.990
That's the way it seemed.

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:23.950
They were banding

00:04:23.960 --> 00:04:26.830
together as Asian

00:04:26.830 --> 00:04:26.840
cultures—North

00:04:26.840 --> 00:04:29.830
Korea trying to bring in

00:04:29.840 --> 00:04:32.990
South Korea in these demonic

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:36.790
spirits, trying to bring in

00:04:36.800 --> 00:04:39.510
Vietnam and the

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:41.430
Philippines, all

00:04:41.430 --> 00:04:41.440
coming

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:46.950
together to combat the Western culture.

00:04:46.960 --> 00:04:48.550
This was part of the vision

00:04:48.560 --> 00:04:49.629
that I was

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:52.590
seeing. I kept hearing 'Pearl

00:04:52.590 --> 00:04:52.600
Harbor'echoing

00:04:52.600 --> 00:04:55.030
in the spirit,

00:04:55.040 --> 00:05:00.270
a retaliation.

00:05:00.280 --> 00:05:05.230
Then the Lord showed

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:07.150
me

00:05:07.160 --> 00:05:10.469
Canada. I started praying for Canada,

00:05:10.479 --> 00:05:13.230
and the Lord showed me the

00:05:13.240 --> 00:05:16.230
scales.

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:19.189
They have been weighed and

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:22.070
found lacking because of the

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:25.670
way the people voted. Not all

00:05:25.680 --> 00:05:29.110
Canadians voted this way. Let me say

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:32.710
