00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:57.029
there was a scale that was tipped in the

00:05:57.039 --> 00:06:00.150
spirit realm.

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:02.390
(That was real thunder as I say this.)

00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:05.550
Wow, Lord, I hear you.

00:06:05.560 --> 00:06:09.189
This is so serious. I saw the

00:06:09.199 --> 00:06:10.590
