00:07:42.160 --> 00:07:45.909
coming onto the scene.

00:07:45.919 --> 00:07:48.749
I

00:07:48.759 --> 00:07:50.749
saw

00:07:50.759 --> 00:07:54.270
judgment begin even in

00:07:54.280 --> 00:07:59.390
