type of virus, a very serious virus

00:08:35.599 --> 00:08:39.310
that is transmitted

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:43.870
through...

00:08:43.880 --> 00:08:47.509
This is very serious.

00:08:47.519 --> 00:08:48.750
I

00:08:48.760 --> 00:08:51.870
saw such a

00:08:51.880 --> 00:08:54.790
